data.description: ON A CLEAR DAY, YOU CAN SEE FOREVER!! NEW ROOF AUG. 2023. This won't be a boring lake view or golf view because views will change continuously. Watch sunrises, sunsets, the milky way or full moon at night while looking down on the Village lights. Live large on the main level with living, dining, gourmet eat in kitchen, primary bedroom and bath, guest bedroom and bath, utility room and 2 car garage. Lower level has another living room, bedroom and full bath that would be ideal for guests, live in help, crafts/hobbies or man cave, and dream workshop. Don't let this one get away!! Lots of new windows and all new interior paint. Buy-in Fee of $1500.00 for new property owners.
